question What language is Scroll written in?

paragraph
 The Scroll CLI app is written in plain Javascript and
 runs in Node.js. Scroll makes heavy use of Tree Languages. The CSS is
 written in Hakonüîójtree.treenotation.org/designer/#standard%20hakon.
 The HTML is written in stumpüîójtree.treenotation.org/designer/#standard%20stump.

paragraph
 TypeScript may be used in the future but Scroll may
 never get over 1kloc so that might not be necessary.

